Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:07.98,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,270)\fad(600,600)}回\N鍋\N肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了  不過我也只能做出這種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害  這不是回鍋肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好肚子餓扁了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在裡面放了一點東西提味  不知你能不能吃出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提味啊  你還真是夠認真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該說是只有豆醬的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是該說提味凸顯得太深了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不如說這個味道越嚼越難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是背道而馳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.97,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N23
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是相當不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紙上：河童  很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何方妖孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童？  為什麼現在要畫河童
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她還說「很帥吧」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她這次畫的畫雖然幻想色彩很強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定某種意義上還算有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡的巨人指宮崎駿著名電影「幽靈公主」裡出場的山神麒麟獸\N原型是日本傳說中的巨人「ダイダラボッチ」，傳說其一晚上就造出了富士山和琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巨人+河童」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  嘿  可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  河童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}河童的發音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAPPA  KAPPA  PA  PA…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就順著這樣開始玩「繪畫接龍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE是這種生物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然畫了這個箭頭  就是說她在邀請我玩「繪畫接龍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就勉為其難玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是PARASITE呢  TE  TE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紙上天狗說的話：時間不夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上文祐子把寄生蟲的日文發音PARASAITO讀成了PARASHITE。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天狗什麼的…  她把PARASITE的TO讀成TE了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了  是天狗呢  天狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GU  GU  GU…  GU！  騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}天狗的日文發音是TENGU，祐子寫成了TENGO。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TENGO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TENGO是什麼玩意啊  TENGO！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  是故意寫錯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生可不會犯這種幼稚的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她在圖上畫了天狗  還特地寫了文字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總覺得無法理解  這裡只能附和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GO來接了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GOKUU-悟空，畫上右下角的字：你給我畫小一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個倦怠的悟空是怎麼回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊咧  悟空？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,360)\fs18}GOKUU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我畫的應該是天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,360)\fs18}TENGU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  心裡想著「GU」卻寫成了「GO」我能夠理解啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下回頭得讓她請客飲料了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  接下來  是U呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U  U…  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紙上：我沒法畫得很好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海膽  不對  是兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,360)\fs18}UNI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,360)\fs18}USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牛嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,360)\fs18}USI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個牛也畫得太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌頭  是舌頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,360)\fs18}SHITA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是TA了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TA  TA  計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,360)\fs18}TAKUSHII
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…什麼鬼東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是TAXI而是TAXY啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  隨便畫個東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美緒把壽司（SUSI）倒過來寫成SI-SU-。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  連業界用語都用上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就好畫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}超人的日語發音「SUUPAAMAN」的結尾為N，無法再接。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  這樣不就輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡  這樣做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}祐子在後面加了個假名ZU，成為SUPERMANS。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.85,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,340)\fad(600,600)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好閑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好閑啊  關口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  關口  來玩「異口同聲」一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我先開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異口同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關口  反正你閑著  偶爾也陪我玩一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  關口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:06.60,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N24
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:15.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}依舊是5-7-5的俳句格式\N最上川是在山形縣的一條河，這裡只是為了湊俳句的格式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘寫作業  罰站在走廊的  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是忘記寫作業了  就被罰站在走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間  要怎樣度過  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  有鹿  有隻鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼校長要把鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…校長  鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  校長他…瀕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  鹿煎餅！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  大家  校長要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣摔下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  DEATH  校長…  DEATH  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…  校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上一切正常！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從心底發出的最真摯的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是因為想包庇校長  或者說是嫌說明麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許只是為了對剛才演出了那場死鬥的勇者們致以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨  過早匯入  最上川  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵…  意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
