Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼  美緒來當裁判哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10円足球不是不需要裁判嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖嘖嘖  你不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是心情的問題  心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都行  攻過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鯊魚「サメ」和韓語的我愛你開頭的發音都是「SA」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.67,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到了一隻蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎…慎重地  總之要慎重地行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓這隻噁心的惡之根源再次在這個家中滋生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計策…必須想出最優計策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  殺蟲劑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是無法一擊殺蟲  就會有讓它逃走的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到它扭曲掙扎的樣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  洗滌劑怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矮腳桌的周圍灑上洗滌劑用於封住它的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再萬無一失地伺機捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  會…會飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是逃走的話這傢伙一定會飛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦飛起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會胡亂地突然飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飛到我身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要是飛向我的臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要是飛到嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飛到嘴裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就給我來一發ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是棒極了  沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起這個碗的一瞬間的選項只有「死」和「死掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH  or  DIE！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…只能那樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阪…阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我  這…這個裡面有蟑…  蟑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是蟑螂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  想要我捉住的話  就把碗打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我就說把碗舉起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話怎麼捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在說什麼啊  居然要我解除這惡之根源的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是潘朵拉之盒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開以後災禍就會降臨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  不把碗打開的話怎麼抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自己打開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼打得開啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的點心是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正是時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一點都不怕蟲  一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  能不能幫我處理一下這個碗裡的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R  R  R  ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼看我一發解決它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明…我明明是如此認真地煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人卻…  這個人卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我最討厭博士了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是騙你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會討厭博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我最喜歡你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真拿博士沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  ROCK'N'ROLL開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:09.10,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,400)}數\N到\N10\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我熱死了  可以出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不是剛剛才進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  數到10就出去怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20㏒√10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數到10了  可以出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「1…2」不這樣數的話不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  大家都說要去補習班  就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有關口一個人  好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  話說關口你不是說要去補習班來著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:13.18,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N26
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  咖喱怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  馬上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經超級餓了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你那裡怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有釣到大魚的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是盛宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  已經差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  超美味超級咖喱完成之卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊還要煮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做咖喱之前準備好的話就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:07.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本俗語「赤子泣くとも蓋取るな」，意為飯煮到一半不准揭蓋。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  畢竟說是「即使小孩哭也不准揭蓋」  啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要是帶蛋黃醬來就好了  果然吃咖喱就是要放蛋黃醬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黃…蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你吃咖喱放什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我嘔～  開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  不是的  這不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你看  我這裡還有涼粉可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼粉…開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}惡搞北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙的血是什麼顏色的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的咖喱和米飯都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼粉的話還有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RELEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這裡還剩下一盒涼粉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一盒嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想讓大家輪流著吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次是我和美緒不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以麻衣你先請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別給我一口全部吃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多慮了  我又不是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先開動嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗆到了
