Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的最後來玩牌  用HAPPY  END來畫上句點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人在這種時候不是要喝酒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  麻衣你會不會那樣想？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也帶來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  美緒你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  就是那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了  這樣就壞了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了！  我要喝啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  快停下  會死的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣你還有多的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是蘋果酒
